result.title: 2018 Topcoder Open Round 1B and Parallel Fun Rated Round
result.content:
The next Algorithm Competition of the 2018 Topcoder Open has arrived! Round 1B will be held on Thursday, May 3, 2018 at 7:00 UTC -4.

Match Editorials: https://www.topcoder.com/blog/2018-tco-algorithm-round-1b-editorials/

The 750 highest scorers from each Round 1 will win a spot in Round 2 of the Algorithm Competition.

Parallel Fun Rated Round: There will also be a Parallel Fun Rated Round for those that aren't eligible or have already advanced to Round 2 for the TCO round

Please note that you must register for the appropriate round in the Arena. Registration opens at 4:00 UTC -4 and closes at 6:55 UTC -4.

Topcoder Applet Guide

Here's the full schedule of TCO18 Rounds

Looking forward to seeing most of you compete :)
